<div class="faq__container">
    <header class="header">
        <div class="header__logo__wrapper">
            <img class="header__logo" src="/img/menu-logo.png" alt="">
            <h2 class="header__title">Talk Time</h2>
        </div>
    </header>
    <div class="faq__content">
        <div class="faq__title__wrapper">
            <h1 class="faq__title">FAQ</h1>
            <span>How to use & frequent questions</span>
        </div>
        <div class="faq__information">
            <div class="faq__wrapper">
                <div class="faq">
                    <span class="faq__text">How to use?</span>
                    <button class="faq__plus faq__button">+</button>
                    <button class="faq__close faq__button">-</button>
                </div>
                <div class="faq__info">
                    <span class="faq__info__text">Install talk time and make sure it is in your chrome extensions. When you are at the meet you can open "Participants" tab and see small green-and-white box in right-bottom corner - it is talk time. Also the new page will be opened, it is VAD (voice activity detection) page, which captures your voice in order to build audio graphs.</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq__wrapper">
                <div class="faq">
                    <span class="faq__text">Is talk time free?</span>
                    <button class="faq__plus faq__button">+</button>
                    <button class="faq__close faq__button">-</button>
                </div>
                <div class="faq__info">
                    <span class="faq__info__text">Talk time is absolutely free, everyone can use it without any payments or providing card details.</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq__wrapper">
                <div class="faq">
                    <span class="faq__text">Switching chrome tabs during the meeting?</span>
                    <button class="faq__plus faq__button">+</button>
                    <button class="faq__close faq__button">-</button>
                </div>
                <div class="faq__info">
                    <span class="faq__info__text">You can switch tab during the meeting in chrome, talk time will be working. Don`t forget to keep your VAD tab open, so that talk time can capture your voice to build audio graph.</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq__wrapper">
                <div class="faq">
                    <span class="faq__text">Features?</span>
                    <button class="faq__plus faq__button">+</button>
                    <button class="faq__close faq__button">-</button>
                </div>
                <div class="faq__info">
                    <span class="faq__info__text">Talk time provides private messaging, ability to send badges during or after meeting, leave feedbacks, view audio activity, percentage of talking time and leave notes about the meeting.</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq__wrapper">
                <div class="faq">
                    <span class="faq__text">Talk time doesn`t display?</span>
                    <button class="faq__plus faq__button">+</button>
                    <button class="faq__close faq__button">-</button>
                </div>
                <div class="faq__info">
                    <span class="faq__info__text">Please make sure that you`ve already installed talk time, and there are not any bugs or errors in your chrome extensions tab. Also talk time works if your chrome language is english, otherwise (for example ukrainian) it won`t work</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq__additional">*If you have other questions, please, <a href="/contacts">Contact Me</a></div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script src="/js/faq.js"></script>